SUMMARY:MARATHON · Sub 3:30 Goal · 30 Aug 2026
DESCRIPTION:Race day! Goal: 3:29:59 · Target pace: 4:58 /km\nStrategy:\n0–5 km: 5:02–5:05 /km (go out conservative)\n5–21 km: 4:58–5:00 /km (settle in)\n21–30 km: 4:58–5:00 /km (stay patient)\n30–42 km: push if legs allow\nHalfway target: 1:44:30–1:45:00\nFuel every 40 min from km 8
